812
00:50:43,280 --> 00:50:46,132
Well, there's a lot to
deal with now that mom--

813
00:50:48,100 --> 00:50:49,423
The funeral.

814
00:50:49,880 --> 00:50:51,145
Her bills.

815
00:50:51,470 --> 00:50:52,494
All her stuff.

816
