820
00:51:17,220 --> 00:51:17,749
No.

821
00:51:19,550 --> 00:51:20,942
Called him this morning.

822
00:51:21,270 --> 00:51:23,283
He said he's waiting
for me to come home.

823
00:51:24,360 --> 00:51:24,855
Nice.

824
00:51:27,910 --> 00:51:28,681
You ever smoked?

825
00:51:30,110 --> 00:51:30,582
No.

826
00:51:31,630 --> 00:51:32,458
You wanna try?

827
00:51:34,360 --> 00:51:36,476
Smoking's really bad for you.

828
00:51:36,640 --> 00:51:38,940
Oh, well, thank you,
Captain Obvious.

829
00:51:43,710 --> 00:51:45,194
So, what kinda
music do you like?

830
00:51:46,560 --> 00:51:47,492
I don't know.

831
00:51:48,120 --> 00:51:48,925
What do you like?

832
00:51:49,160 --> 00:51:49,747
Mm.

833
00:51:50,710 --> 00:51:51,573
Clash

834
00:51:51,670 --> 00:51:52,613
Social D

835
00:51:52,760 --> 00:51:53,669
The Replacements.

