841
00:52:03,540 --> 00:52:04,023
Yeah.

842
00:52:04,640 --> 00:52:05,526
Are you kidding?

843
00:52:07,460 --> 00:52:07,932
No.

844
00:52:11,030 --> 00:52:12,226
