That her old T-Bird?

846
00:52:25,200 --> 00:52:25,798
Yeah.

847
00:52:27,300 --> 00:52:30,014
I remember the day
she drove that off the lot.

848
00:52:31,040 --> 00:52:33,547
So proud of her
shiny new car.

849
00:52:34,480 --> 00:52:35,101
Montine.

850
00:52:36,630 --> 00:52:38,769
