851
00:52:39,820 --> 00:52:41,327
And you need to be there.

852
00:52:41,550 --> 00:52:42,148
[scoffs]

853
00:52:45,090 --> 00:52:48,880
You go on and throw a big
shindig at the church, Billy boy.

854
00:52:48,900 --> 00:52:50,326
That's what
you need to do.

855
00:52:51,070 --> 00:52:51,714
[chuckles]

856
00:52:52,890 --> 00:52:54,972
Said my goodbyes long time ago.

857
00:52:56,950 --> 00:52:58,089
I won't be there.

858
00:52:58,890 --> 00:53:00,374
I don't need to be there.

859
00:53:02,790 --> 00:53:04,826
What if I told you I
needed you here?

860
00:53:07,240 --> 00:53:09,414
I'll probably tell
you to deal with it.

861
00:53:13,900 --> 00:53:17,736
Just for one time if you could think
about someone other than yourself.

862
00:53:17,760 --> 00:53:19,876
Well, that's rich
coming from you.

863
00:53:20,760 --> 00:53:22,048
Oh, yeah, you're right.

864
00:53:22,630 --> 00:53:23,838
I'm not perfect.

865
00:53:24,400 --> 00:53:25,458
I've sinned.

866
00:53:26,270 --> 00:53:27,696
And I've been humbled.

867
00:53:27,800 --> 00:53:28,596
But I'll tell you what.

868
00:53:28,620 --> 00:53:31,676
I've been here with
my mom day after day,

869
00:53:31,700 --> 00:53:34,606
feeding her, talking to
her, changing her diapers.

870
00:53:34,630 --> 00:53:38,096
Oh ho, so you win the
best child of the year award?

871
00:53:38,120 --> 00:53:40,512
I'm not looking to win an award.

872
00:53:42,140 --> 00:53:43,635
I did it for love.

873
00:53:46,820 --> 00:53:48,603
Do you remember what love is?

874
00:53:54,950 --> 00:53:57,296
- If Michael were here--
- Yeah, but he's not.

875
00:53:57,500 --> 00:53:58,466
He's gone.

876
00:53:58,990 --> 00:54:01,926
And there's nothing
that you or your prayers

877
00:54:01,950 --> 00:54:06,470
