bring him or mom or any of them back.

878
00:54:07,250 --> 00:54:10,643
You just go on preaching
and preaching, man.

879
00:54:11,530 --> 00:54:13,405
It seems to be
what you're good at.

880
00:54:23,700 --> 00:54:27,104
[music]

881
00:54:27,650 --> 00:54:31,326
[indistinct chattering]

882
00:54:31,350 --> 00:54:32,753
Quit staring at people.

883
00:54:33,680 --> 00:54:34,347
Sorry.

884
00:54:37,300 --> 00:54:38,151
Where's your mom?

885
00:54:39,910 --> 00:54:42,130
She left us.
Two years ago.

886
00:54:42,850 --> 00:54:44,115
Why would she leave you?

887
00:54:45,800 --> 00:54:46,444
Well.

888
00:54:46,530 --> 00:54:48,456
When my dad was a
new preacher in town,

889
00:54:48,480 --> 00:54:52,781
