1049
01:06:04,630 --> 01:06:06,776
It's just a kid. He's
excited to see his father.

1050
01:06:06,800 --> 01:06:08,790
His father ain't been
home since Tuesday.

1051
01:06:09,940 --> 01:06:10,768
Tuesday?

1052
01:06:10,960 --> 01:06:12,306
He worked at the Trade Center.

1053
01:06:13,730 --> 01:06:14,823
It's a shame, really.

1054
01:06:14,930 --> 01:06:16,310
He seemed like a nice guy.

1055
01:06:16,980 --> 01:06:17,624
[door closes]

1056
